Detailed Description

Saves a celltree to an xml file, by converting cell structure to XML.

Date:
2005-11-30 (update)
Traverses the cellstructure and creates a serialized stream of the internal representation of the document.

2005-11-30 AF, This class was remade when another xml format was used to save the cell structure.
